    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but when you look at the actual trends, do the numbers suggest that these disincentives are a significant factor? like, is there a measurable trend of people opting out of the workforce because of the benefits? i'm seeing a lot of debate online about whether it's actually a major driver of the labor shortage.",
