      "content": "i hear you, but it feels like you're kind of dismissing the other side's point. if the benefits are high enough, wouldn't it be a logical, fact-based conclusion that some people would choose not to work? why do you think that's just a \"simplistic narrative\" rather than a valid economic concern?",
